import Vue from 'vue'
import Router from 'vue-router'
import HelloContainer from "./components/HelloWorld.vue"
import Home from "./components/weixin/Home.vue"
import Footer from "./components/weixin/common/footer.vue"
import Destination from "./components/weixin/common/Destination.vue"
import login from "./components/weixin/common/login.vue"
import reg from "./components/weixin/common/reg.vue"
import mine from "./components/weixin/common/mine.vue"
import index from "./components/weixin/common/index.vue"
import TabBarIcon from "./components/weixin/common/TabBarIcon.vue"
import add from "./components/weixin/common/add.vue"
import aftermine from "./components/weixin/common/aftermine.vue"
import Dingzhi from "./components/weixin/common/Dingzhi.vue"

Vue.use(Router)
export default new Router({
  routes: [
    {path:'/Home',component:Home},
    {path:'/',component:HelloContainer},
    {path:'/footer',component:Footer},
    {path:'/login',component:login},
    {path:'/reg',component:reg},
    {path:'/index',component:index},
    {path:'/Destination',component:Destination},
    {path:'/TabBarIcon',component:TabBarIcon},
    {path:'/add',component:add},
    {path:'/mine',component:mine},
    {path:'/aftermine',component:aftermine},
    {path:'/dingzhi',component:Dingzhi},
  ]
})
